					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "A summarizer defines a concise text through {{gtMethod:GtLToolCallsSummarizer>>#summaryText}} and one or more {{gtPragma:gtView}} views. The default summary view is {{gtMethod:GtLToolCallsSummarizer>>#gtSummaryFor:}}."
