				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Concrete summarizers select relevant tool calls and compute domain objects from them. For example, {{gtClass:GtLCodeChangesToolCallsSummarizer}} summarizes code-modifying tool calls and exposes views such as {{gtMethod:GtLCodeChangesToolCallsSummarizer>>#gtPackageChangeHistoriesFor:}} and {{gtMethod:GtLCodeChangesToolCallsSummarizer>>#gtCodeChangesFor:}}."
			},
